{
  "stem": "14156.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 442.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You can stay now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was the first break, I would say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from there, we got loaded up in military trucks, no tarp on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The side on-- on the trucks was about that high.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to hold on, one to each other, so we wouldn't fall out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the sky was clear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I see the stars.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to myself, God, what did I do?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm just a young man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm only 18.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm no criminal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was my thoughts, OK?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told him, God, please, just register that that's how I feel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That was that episode.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came-- then we came into-- it was a-- was a-- what they called [GERMAN], another smaller camp, what was called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came in there, out of the trucks, into a-- into a wash room with showers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had showers up on top.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody-- everything out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Except you keep your boots.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything else, you just put on the side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a watch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Grandma used to give me that watch for bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was an eight-corner watch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I felt, they're not going to get that watch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were-- there were wash basins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I took the watch, and I smashed it in there, so nobody could ever use it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they-- they said, OK, under the shower.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There is a piece of soap.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The soap has to last for five, six people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "First of all, we make you wet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, when the water came down, it was cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And then finally, it got warm, a little warm, and then they screamed, hurry up!",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Soap yourself in, fast!",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
